### Get all birds
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds

### Get one bird
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/1

### Get non-existent bird
GET http://localhost:8787/api/birds/999

### Create a bird (valid)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "common_name": "Curve-billed Thrasher",
  "scientific_name": "Toxostoma curvirostre",
  "family": "Mimidae"
}

### Create a bird (missing required field)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scientific_name": "Corvus brachyrhynchos"
}

### Create a bird (unknown field — strictObject rejects)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/birds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "common_name": "American Crow",
  "wingspan_cm": 100
}

### Patch a bird
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/birds/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "A striking whistling-duck with a bold chestnut and black body, often nesting in tree cavities."
}

### Patch with empty body (should fail)
PATCH http://localhost:8787/api/birds/3
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Delete a bird
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/birds/5

### Delete non-existent bird
DELETE http://localhost:8787/api/birds/999